runexp /kst/exp/ipy/ipy 06 ip2

This is an experiment to study the response of the polar ionosphere to a solar 
eclipse. Supportive measurements include the ISACCO GPS scintillation 
receivers and MIDAS tomography measurement for cross-calibration of TEC 
values. In addition, large-scale TEC maps from DLR are available. 
